==== Inviting opposite wide-range 1NT

@ Only applies vs major

The wide-range 1NT means that responder has two ranges of invitations. +
@ a *strong invitation* {thinsp}({simto}11 HCP)
_ is only declined with a min +
@ a *weak invitation* {thinsp}({simto}9 HCP)
