=== Vs 2NT-Opening = minors

[green-box]#Added {ndash} July 14, 2019#

A 2NT opening showing a weak hand with both minors is part of Fantunes
and Polish Club.
Some strong-1{C} pairs also play it.

&Our defence&

Pass with both minors.  A subsequent double is penalty.

Double shows values but not both minors.
#We have NOT established the balance-of-power# so a subsequent double
